Installation

-> copy the basefile and folder to the skins/ dir of your mediaWiki install
-> change name of default theme in ./LocalSettings.php
-> reload mediaWiki

Top navigation menu

-> changes to the top menu must be made manually in the file at ./wikistrap/menu.php
